author: iik1997
body:
See discussion in #12544 and #12570. This update should help to avoid crashes of Castor online DQM  in case if recent modifications of Castor/ZDC unpackers in 75X are going to be propagated also to 76X (and 80X).
@popovvp, @cbaus, @vanbesien,  @hvanhaev
title: Cleanup and update to stay in sync with modifications done in 75X
